reviewText:
I love these old movies.  I remember some of them from TV and have some favorites.  So far, all the dvd's have been excellent quality.  I have watched 10 of the movies so far, 5 Dics.

I have watched all but the last two dvd's.  All the ones with Raymond Burr so far.  All the DVD's have been of fine quality.
I am a Perry Mason fan
